iZAP-open-login
------------------------
### Description 
   The iZAP-open-login plugin enable the user visitng your site to register through other popular
   social media sites like Facebook, Yahoo, Google.
    
### Features
1. Give users the facility to login through there facebook, yahoo, or google accounts

### Dependencies and other important instruction    
1. Izap-elgg-bridge must be activated and the same can be get from > [Pluginlotto](http://www.pluginlotto.com).
2. Read INSTALL before installation.
    
